Package: iNEXT.IE
Type: Package
Title: Interpolation and Extrapolation for Inter-specific Encounter
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Kai-Hsiang Hu [aut, cre], Anne Chao [ctb]
Maintainer: KaiHsiang Hu <river19951224@gmail.com>
